  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>In v1.10, all the bugs found earlier have been fixed.Community players select different characters to complete the game.Please rest assured.<br>V1.10 also adds heroic dungeons, new martial arts and spells to increase late game challenge and playability.</u></h2></strong><br><br>Email: <a href=\"mailto:elec2015@126.com\">elec2015@126.com</a><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike Or RPG？</strong></h2>\tEvery time a Du jie fails, it is reincarnation, a \"resurrection\" of Roguelike. <br><br>A unique Roguelike.<br>       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/1a4daf50e27b53e6a073fc6d4b3a8537.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/2750b6202bf7856e7cc037ffcb55fb21.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br>        <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\t<strong>Single-player Or Online Games?</strong></h2>\t6 cyclic, unlimited tasks<br><br>\t5 instance zones are divided into 3 difficulty levels and 15 challenges<br>\t18 plot combats from Journey to the west<br>\t20+ herbal materials<br>\tMore than 100 basic equipments<br>\tMore than 20 kinds of BUFF with 5 kinds of quality have developed countless equipments<br>\tA rich single-player game that extends your gaming experience<br>\t<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/f4a489656d8f03ff78e99fea08d59020.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/02b62475a4b1630317f3d1d7f5fa2b49.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/c79bf0ca718a1537105af46cd5e56023.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/e86c4e583616b3e3befcfb5eecff3c02.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\t<strong>Protagonist Or NPC?</strong></h2>\tThey also do tasks, instance zones, build equipment...<br><br>You'll even be invited to explore the instance zones<br>Autonomous NPCS<br>\t<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/6ed027b1b2c9f72779f7fae5a1e85440.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/b8f3a1b862801dbee08024a05a7d1404.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  \t<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/5a6705bb7113100f28e3cfb95d21e97c.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\t<strong>Round Or Strategy?</strong></h2>\tDifferent skill combinations to get a different BUFF: bleed, break armor, heal, fight...<br><br>80+ spells & skills<br>100+ skill mix<br>Cannot count skill learning configurations<br>\t<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/cecfb2a5c0c40b2ff724cfa5d8891b15.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/b63b6831c8b5326220126ae9c5ba70d6.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https: